msg: ra_serf: Fix API bug when fetched_rev is non-NULL and revision is invalid.

author: hwright
msg: Only force the calculation of a file checksum if the fs does not return the
kind of checksum the caller asked for.
(svn_fs_file_checksum):  Fetch the checksum from the FS first, and only if
the returned value is NULL or the kind isn't what we want, manually
calculate the desired type of checksum.
